text.tspan: Click the encoder knob in when at the home screen
HOME - Returns to the home screen.
Mode - Switches between single note and sequencer
Scale Type - Change the scale which notes are
selected from. "None" means the same note is
always played. Use "Chromatic" to play all notes
Root Note - Selects the root note of the scale,
Range - The number of octaves of the selected scale
Min/Max Velocity: Change the upper and lower limits
of the range of velocities to play notes at. Set
these to be equal for no velocity variation.
Note length: The length (in ms) to play each note
